WEBVTT

00:03.434 --> 00:06.887
I didn't wash my hands,
and I don't care.

00:06.888 --> 00:08.653
Yup.

00:08.654 --> 00:12.634
Cool to be some place
right when things get good, right?

00:13.961 --> 00:17.532
Another pitcher of
your strongest beer, please, good sir,

00:17.533 --> 00:20.224
and a glass thingie
to drink it out of.

00:20.225 --> 00:24.546
And one of whatever
this guy's having for that guy,

00:24.547 --> 00:27.069
and one of what
that guy's having for this guy.

00:27.235 --> 00:29.818
And another round for everyone, on me!

00:30.987 --> 00:32.720
That's right.
That's right.

00:32.722 --> 00:34.823
- Thanks, buddy.
- What's the occasion?

00:34.858 --> 00:36.759
Oh, I'm celebrating.

00:36.760 --> 00:40.963
My name's Jake Peralta,
and I just got fired from the NYPD.

00:40.964 --> 00:44.751
